room_title: Escape room "Zombie Nursery" by Lights Out Escape Rooms in Denver
room_address: 1500 W Littleton Blvd Unit 110 C/D Littleton, CO 80120
room_description: What could be more fun than babysitting a horde of zombie babies? Surviving would be nice. Your group of friends has decided to take on an evening of babysitting, in the hopes of earning some extra cash. What the parents failed to mention, is that their bundles of joy are actually brain-eating babies. To earn your pay for the night, you must complete the tasks that the parents left for you and most importantly, be alive to accept your pay.
